”Alexa, ask u. s. president fact to say me president three”
”Alexa, ask u. s. president fact to give me president fact forty three”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: u. s. president fact
des: The skill introduces all us presidents by querying with the order of them. When the skill is launched, the latest president is introduced. When user asks from the skill with the any of the given intents, the number is requested from the user. This number represents the order of the presidents. If the number is greater than the total president number, then the user will be informed about the limitations.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
